com.playground.payroll.domain

Class IncomeTaxRate

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.playground.payroll.domain.IncomeTaxRate

  • @Entity
public class IncomeTaxRate
extends java.lang.Object
    JPA Entity for the income tax rates (brackets). These are used to calculate an employees income tax based on their annual salary. Each tax rate is for a particular amount of the annual salary.
    Version:
    %I%, %G%
    Author:
    Justin Taylor
